Petroleum Geo - Services registers offering . Petroleum Geo - Services said it filed a registration statement with the U . S . Securities and Exchange Commission for an offering of 4 . 6 million American Depositary Shares , representing the same number of ordinary shares of the company . It said the ADRs will be included in the Nasdaq National Market , and the Ordinary shares are listed on the Oslo Stock Exchange . Proceeds will be used to expand its library of 3D multi - client seismic data , to repay outstanding debt under various credit facilities and general corporate purposes . The company said the offering will be made outside Norway , and is to be led by Prudential Securities , Donaldson Lufkin & Jenrette , Salomon Brothers , Simmons & Co and Cambridge Partners LLC . - - New York Newsdesk 212 859 1610 
